query:
INSERT INTO trip_routes (tripId, name, nameHe, description, descriptionHe, date, time, distanceKm, estimatedDuration, roadType, mapData, createdAt, updatedAt)
SELECT 2 as tripId, name, nameHe, description, descriptionHe, date, time, distanceKm, estimatedDuration, roadType, mapData, NOW() as createdAt, NOW() as updatedAt
FROM trip_routes
WHERE tripId = 1;
